        <updateDate>2021-01-15T18:28:51Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Comprehensive Addiction Resources Emergency Act of 2019</b><br> <br> This bill establishes various programs to address substance use disorder and opioid addiction, including grants for treatment, recovery, and harm reduction services as well as a program to distribute overdose reversal drugs.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
